data.title: Lunch with associates
data.text: Food was very good & for the price of other similar places, you got a lot. Plenty of food. Enjoyed their special fish taco & shared there BBQ Mix plate. Plenty! Mon-Thurs they have special lunch deal. One for each day. Don't forget to try the Loco Moco or the Kalua Pork. Take a chance and try if your feeling for a Hawaiian plate. They also carry soda from the island. Limited seating in doors.

data.title: Good and Generous Portion of Kalua Pork and Cabbage - Yum!
data.text:
I enjoyed their kalua pork and cabbage for dinner.  It came with macaroni salad and rice.  Portion size was generous.   It smelled and tasted very good.

Service was superb for this order at the counter type place.  Staff was friendly, helpful and superb  Good job!

Price is very reasonable.

Parking is free.  It is in the Pacific Commons Shopping area of Fremont.

data.title: slice of Hawaii, good bbq beef but the macaroni is not as good as L&L
